text: Guy Creighton (born 1 September 1949) is an Australian equestrian. He competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics and the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Australia Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics
